    var doMapOpts = { center: new google.maps.LatLng(0,0), zoom: 13, disableDefaultUI: true, panControl: true, zoomControl: true, mapTypeControl: false, scaleControl: false, streetViewControl: false, overviewMapControl: false, mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP };

    

    var pickupMap = null;
    var dropoffMap = null;

    var puSearchMarker = null;
    var doSearchMarker = null;

    var puMarkers = new Array();
    var doMarkers = new Array();

    var redIcon = "/images/site_graphics/newsite/map_pointer.png";
    var blueIcon = "/images/site_graphics/newsite/pin-car-b.png";
    var blueAirportIcon = "/images/site_graphics/newsite/pin-airport-b.png";

    //Get a list of options selected, using checkboxes, within the specified jQuery selector
    function getCheckboxParamValue(container) {
        var checkedValues = [];
        $("input:checkbox", $(container)).each(function() {
            if($(this).is(":checked") == true && !checkedValues.includes($(this).val()))
                checkedValues.push($(this).val());
        });
        return checkedValues.join(':');
    }

    //Attach regular toggle and filter events to all checkboxes in a specific selector
    //If "includeParametersWhenAllSelected" is true, all values from checkboxes will be taken even if they are all selected
    function attachCheckboxEvents(selector, paramName, logLabel, includeParametersWhenAllSelected) {
        var checkboxes = $('input:checkbox', $(selector));

        //Attach filter event
        checkboxes.bind('filter', function() {
            if ($(this).parent().attr('num') != 0) {
                var normalizedFilterName = mapFilterParamNameToNormalizedName(paramName);
                ajaxSetCookie({name: 'srvi', value: 'filter-' + (normalizedFilterName === null ? '' : normalizedFilterName)});
                $('form[name="ComplexFiltersForm"]').submit(function () {
                    fillInFilterInputValue(paramName, getCheckboxParamValue(selector, includeParametersWhenAllSelected));
                });
                submitForm(this);
            }
        });

        //Toggle input state without triggering event
        checkboxes.bind('toggle', function() {
            $(this).attr('checked', !$(this).is(':checked'));
        });

        //Attach click event
        checkboxes.click(function() {
            
            try {
                GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', logLabel, getCheckboxParamValue(selector, includeParametersWhenAllSelected), 1, true);
            } catch (err) {}

            $(this).trigger('toggle');
            $(this).trigger('filter');
        });
    }

    

    function applyFilter(paramName, paramValue, logLabel, enteredValue) {
        if ($(this).parent().attr('num') != 0) {
            var normalizedFilterName = mapFilterParamNameToNormalizedName(paramName);
            ajaxSetCookie({name: 'srvi', value: 'filter-' + (normalizedFilterName === null ? '' : normalizedFilterName)});
            $('form[name="ComplexFiltersForm"]').submit(function () {
                fillInFilterInputValue(paramName, paramValue);
            });
            if (paramValue !== '') {
                try {
                    GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent',
                        'SearchResultsFilters',
                        logLabel,
                        'sent = ' + paramValue + ' entered = ' + enteredValue,
                        1,
                        true);
                } catch (err) {
                }
            }
            submitForm(this);

        }
    }

    function mapFilterParamNameToNormalizedName(paramName) {
        if (paramName === 'b_spl') {
            return 'supplier';
        }
        if (paramName === 's_rating') {
            return 'rating';
        }
        if (paramName === 'filterLocType') {
            return 'locationType';
        }
        if (paramName === 'filterFuel') {
            return 'fuelType';
        }
        if (paramName === 'filterAircon') {
            return 'aircon';
        }
        if (paramName === 'filterTransmission') {
            return 'transmission';
        }
        
        if (paramName === 'doors') {
            return 'doors';
        }
        if (paramName === 'fuelType') {
            return 'diesel';
        }
        if (paramName === 'groupSize') {
            return 'groupSize';
        }
        if (paramName === 'filterPrice') {
            return 'price';
        }
        if (paramName === 'filterManufacturer') {
            return 'manufacturer';
        }
        return null;
    }

    function submitForm(obj) {
        if(submitTimeout!=null)
            clearTimeout(submitTimeout);

        submitTimeout = setTimeout(function() {
            fillInFilterInputValue("filterAdditionalInfo",getAdditionalInfoParamValue());
            fillInFilterInputValue("advSearch",getAdvSearchParamValue());
            fillInFilterInputValue("exSuppliers",getExSuppliersValues());
            

            $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").submit();
        }, 0);
    }

</script>

<script nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
            var collapseFiltersDocReady = function() {
                $('.filter_title_container').click(function() {
                    $(this).parent('.filter-group').toggleClass('collapsed');

                    var filterCategory = $(this).parent().attr('class').split(' ')[1];

                    // Define in the tracker when the user opens or closes the specific category filter
                    if ($(this).parent().hasClass('collapsed')) {
                        GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'SearchResults', filterCategory, 'close', 1, true);
                        
                    } else {
                        GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'SearchResults', filterCategory, 'open', 1, true);
                        
                    }

                });
            };

            
            $(document).ready(collapseFiltersDocReady);
            </script>

</div> <script nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
        
        doGALog = function(){};

        
        var filterRefreshDocReady = function() {
            $('.filter_refresh .refresh, .reset_filters > a').click(function (){
                try {
                    GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', 'resetFilters', $(this).is('.reset_filters > a') ? 'zeroSearch' : 'complexFilter', 1, true);
                } catch (err) {}

                var form = $("form[name=SearchResultsForm]");
                form.attr("action","SearchResults.do");
                var a=form.find("[name\x3demptySearchResults]");
                0==a.length?form.append('\x3cinput type\x3d"hidden" name\x3d"emptySearchResults" value\x3d"false" /\x3e'):a.attr("value","false");

                
                ajaxSetCookie({name: 'srvi', value: 'filter-showAll'});
                form.submit();
            });
        };

        
        $(document).ready(filterRefreshDocReady);
        

        $(".filter-group input[type='checkbox']").click(function() {
            var filterGroupSection = $(this).closest(".filter-group").attr("data-filter-group-name");
            if(filterGroupSection) {
                var filterGroupName = "Filter Group - " + filterGroupSection;
                var filterState = $(this).is(":checked") ? "Selected" : "Deselected";
                var filterValue = "(" + $(this).attr("name") + ") " + $(this).val();
                try {
                    GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', filterGroupName, filterState, filterValue, 1, true);
                } catch (err) { }
            }
        });
    </script>
<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
        function customCheckboxInit(){
            var checkboxes = jQuery171(".filters input[type='checkbox']");
            checkboxes.iCheck({
                checkboxClass: 'checkbox',
                checkedClass: 'checked',
                disabledClass: 'disabled'
            });
            checkboxes.on('ifClicked', function(event){
                $(this).first().click();

            });

            var label = $('.filters ul li label');
            label.css('padding','0');
            label.css('background','none');

            var activeLabels = $('.filters ul li:not(.filter_disabled) label');
            activeLabels.parent('li').attr('tabindex', 0).keydown(function(event) {
                var $this = $(this);
                var SPACEBAR = 32;
                var ENTER_KEY = 13;
                var keycode = event.keyCode || event.which;
                if (keycode == ENTER_KEY || keycode == SPACEBAR) {
                    $this.find('label').trigger('click');
                    event.preventDefault();
                }
            });
        }

        customCheckboxInit();

        $(function() {
            $('.filters').removeClass('filters--loading');
        });
    </script>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            
            setTimeout(function(){
                $('.map-hint').show();
            }, 5000);

            setTimeout(function(){
                $('.map-hint').fadeOut();
            }, 15000);
            

            $('.inline-message.hide-on a.hide').click(function (){
                $(this).parent().removeClass('zoomInUp').addClass('zoomOutDown').fadeOut();
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-879', 'Close hint', 'closed', 1, true);
            });
            
            if ($('body').hasClass('filter')) {
                $('.bui-filter-open').removeClass('bui-hide');
                $('.bui-filter-open').addClass('bui-show');
            } else {
                $('.bui-filter-closed').removeClass('bui-hide');
                $('.bui-filter-closed').addClass('bui-show');
            }
            
        });
    </script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
                    function saveQuotePopup(vehicleId, previousPrice, rateReference, locId, dropLocId, locName, dropLocName, countryEn) {
                        GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'Quote button clicked', vehicleId, 1, true);

                        var data = {};

                        $('form[name="BookingExtrasForm"] input').each(function() {
                            data[$(this).attr('name')] = $(this).val();
                        });

                        data['layout'] = 'quotePopup';
                        data['previousPrice'] = previousPrice;
                        data['vehicleInfo.vehicle.rateReference'] = rateReference;
                        data['vehicleInfo.vehicle.id'] = vehicleId;
                        data['vehicleInfo.supplier.locId'] = locId;
                        data['vehicleInfo.supplier.dropLocId'] = dropLocId;
                        data['locationName'] = locName;
                        data['dropLocationName'] = dropLocName;
                        data['location'] = locId;
                        data['dropLocation'] = dropLocId;
                        data['countryEn'] = countryEn;

                        //Open the quote popup and set necessary information to fulfill the request
                        $.ajax({
                            url: "/QuotePopupAction.do",
                            async: true,
                            data: data,
                            type: 'POST',
                            success: function(data) {
                                $('.quote-loading').hide();
                                if($.trim(data) !== '') {
                                    $('<div/>').html(data)
                                        .lightbox_me({
                                            centered: true,
                                            closeClick: false,
                                            overlayCSS: {
                                                background: '#000',
                                                opacity: 0.4
                                            },
                                            fitInScreen: true,
                                            destroyOnClose: true,
                                            onLoad: function() {
                                                if(typeof assignQuoteValidationEvents != 'undefined') assignQuoteValidationEvents();
                                            }
                                        });
                                }
                                else {
                                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'VehicleNotFound', '', 1, true);
                                }
                            },
                            error: function(jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown){
                                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'quotePopupAjaxError', 'ajaxError', 1, true);
                                if(jqXHR){
                                    var errorcode = 'ErrorCode:'+jqXHR.status;
                                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'quotePopupAjaxErrorCode', errorcode, 1, true);
                                }
                            }
                        });

                    }

                    function attachTooltipEvents(_this, message, classes) {
                        $(_this).mouseover(function() {
                            var messageTooltip = message;
                            tooltipshow(_this,'', messageTooltip,undefined,undefined,{style:{classes: classes}});
                        }).mouseout(function() {
                            tooltipshow(_this);
                        });
                    }

                    $(document).ready(function(){
                        $('.carResultDiv [data-tooltip]').each(function(){
                            var message = $(this).data('tooltip');
                            var tooltipClass = $(this).data('tooltip-class');
                            attachTooltipEvents($(this),message,tooltipClass);
                        });

                        
                    });

                    
                    function trackBookNow() {
                        GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'RACSB-112', 'Book Now Button', 'Clicked', 1, true);
                    }
                    </script>

                                function showBookingAjaxRatings(clickedElem, supplierName, supplierImageLrgPath, locNameEng, cityEn, countryEn, locName, vehicleId, locId, dropLocId, ratingMessage, numberOfRatings, roundedAverage) {
                                    var eventData = {
                                        category: '_trackEvent',
                                        action: 'FE-5350',
                                        label: 'showRatings',
                                        info: '',
                                        value: 1
                                    };

                                    $.ajax({
                                        async:true,
                                        url: '/ActionEventAction.do',
                                        data: eventData
                                    });
                                    var data = {};
                                    
                                        data['layout'] = 'bookingRatingsModalV2';
                                        data['lang'] = 391;
                                        data['enableReviewRatings'] = false;
                                    
                                    data['supplierName'] = supplierName;
                                    data['supplierImageLrgPath'] = supplierImageLrgPath;
                                    data['locNameEng'] = locNameEng;
                                    data['cityEn'] = cityEn;
                                    data['countryEn'] = countryEn;
                                    data['locName'] = locName;
                                    data['vehicleId'] = vehicleId;
                                    data['locId'] = locId;
                                    data['dropLocId'] = dropLocId;
                                    data['ratingMessage'] = ratingMessage;
                                    data['numberOfRatings'] = numberOfRatings;
                                    data['averageRating'] = roundedAverage;

                                    $.ajax({
                                        url: '/RequestData.do',
                                        async: true,
                                        data: data,
                                        type: 'POST',
                                        success: function(data) {
                                            $('#bookingReviewModal-content', 'div#bookingReviewModal').html(data);
                                        }
                                    });
                                }

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
  (function () {
    var protocolValue = "";
    if (protocolValue && typeof(ADRUM) != "undefined") {
      ADRUM.command("addUserData", "protocol", protocolValue);
    }
  }());

  $( document ).ready(function() {
    function logProtocolInGA (){
      var protocolValue = "";
      var protocolCustomVariableName = "Visit Protocol";
      if (protocolValue && typeof(_gaq) != "undefined") {
        //Set custom variable 'Visit Protocol' on page level in Google Analytics
        //use custom variable slot 47
        _gaq.push(['_setCustomVar', 47, protocolCustomVariableName , protocolValue, 3 ]);
        _gaq.push(['_trackEvent', protocolCustomVariableName, 'visited' ]);
      }
    }
    logProtocolInGA();
  });
</script>





<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">

    function showAjaxRatingModal(clickedElem, supplierName, supplierImageLrgPath, locNameEng, cityEn, countryEn, locName, vehicleId, locId, dropLocId) {
        GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'showRatings', supplierName, 1, true);
        clickedElem.css('cursor','progress');

        var data = {};

        data['layout'] = 'ratingsModal';
        data['supplierName'] = supplierName;
        data['supplierImageLrgPath'] = supplierImageLrgPath;
        data['locNameEng'] = locNameEng;
        data['cityEn'] = cityEn;
        data['countryEn'] = countryEn;
        data['locName'] = locName;
        data['vehicleId'] = vehicleId;
        data['locId'] = locId;
        data['dropLocId'] = dropLocId;

        
        data['location'] = locId;
        data['dropLocation'] = dropLocId;
        data['locationName'] = locName;
        data['dropLocationName'] = locName;
        

        $.ajax({
            url: "/RequestData.do",
            async: true,
            data: data,
            type: 'POST',
            success: function(data) {
                if($.trim(data) !== ''){
                    var lightboxDiv = $('<div class="pop-up_outline supplierInfoPopup supplierInfoPopup--bui" style="display:none;"/>');
                    lightboxDiv.append(data);
                    lightboxDiv.lightbox_me({
                        centered: true,
                        overlayCSS: {background: '#fff', opacity: 0.8},
                        destroyOnClose: true,
                        lightboxSpeed: 'slow'
                    });
                }
                else{
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'emptyData', '', 1, true);
                }
            },
            error: function(jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown){
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'ratingModalAjaxError', 'ajaxError', 1, true);
                if(jqXHR){
                    var errorcode = 'ErrorCode:'+jqXHR.status;
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'ratingModalAjaxError', errorcode, 1, true);
                }
            },
            complete: function(jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown){
                clickedElem.css('cursor','pointer');
            }
        });


    }

    function showAjaxRatings(clickedElem, supplierName, locNameEng, cityEn, countryEn, locName, vehicleId, locId, dropLocId) {

        $.ajax({

            success: function(data) {

<script nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
    RCMap.MapMarker.prototype.draw = function() {

        var overlayProjection = this.getProjection();

        var pixelPosition = overlayProjection.fromLatLngToDivPixel(this.bounds_);

        var div = this.div_;
        var $div = $(div);

        div.style.left = (pixelPosition.x - $div.width()/2) + 'px';
        div.style.top = (pixelPosition.y - $div.height()) + 'px';
    };

    RCMap.MapIcon.prototype.draw = function() {

        var overlayProjection = this.getProjection();

        var pixelPosition = overlayProjection.fromLatLngToDivPixel(this.bounds_);

        var div = this.div_;
        var $div = $(div);
        div.style.left = (pixelPosition.x - $div.width()/2) + 'px';
        div.style.top = (pixelPosition.y - $div.height()/2) + 'px';
    };

    RCMap.MapLabel.prototype.draw = function() {

        var overlayProjection = this.getProjection();

        var pixelPosition = overlayProjection.fromLatLngToDivPixel(this.bounds_);

        var div = this.div_;
        var $div = $(div);
        div.style.left = (pixelPosition.x - $div.width()/2) + 'px';
        div.style.top = (pixelPosition.y - $div.height()) + 'px';
    };

    RCMap.MapMarker.prototype.onAdd = function() {
        var this_ = this;
        var div = document.createElement('div');
        div.style.border = 'none';
        div.style.borderWidth = '0px';
        div.style.position = 'absolute';
        div.title = this.title_;
        div.style.zIndex = this.zIndex_;
        if (typeof(this.className) != "undefined") {
            div.className = this.className;
        } else {
            div.className = 'mapMarker';
        }

        var img = document.createElement('img');
        img.src = this.icon_;
        img.width = 32;
        img.height = 32;

        div.appendChild(img);
        this.div_ = div;

        google.maps.event.addDomListener(this_.div_, "click", function (e) {
            google.maps.event.trigger(this_, "click", e);
            RCMap.cAbortEvent(e); // Prevent click from being passed on to map
        });
        google.maps.event.addDomListener(this.div_, "dblclick", function (e) {
            google.maps.event.trigger(this_, "dblclick", e);
            RCMap.cAbortEvent(e); // Prevent map zoom when double-clicking on a label
        });

        google.maps.event.addDomListener(this.div_,'mouseover', function() {
            rcMap.highlightMarker(this_.lat_+","+this_.lon_, true, true);

            function triggerScrollListToView() {
                scrollListToView(this_.lat_+","+this_.lon_);
            }
            if(rcMap.rowIconhighlightedCallback != null) {
                rcMap.rowIconhighlightedCallback(this_.lat_ + "," + this_.lon_, true, true);
            }

            clearTimeout(RCMap.MapLabel.timeout_);
            RCMap.MapLabel.timeout_ = setTimeout(triggerScrollListToView, 300);
        });

        google.maps.event.addDomListener(this.div_,'mouseout', function() {
            clearTimeout(RCMap.MapLabel.timeout_);

            if(rcMap.rowIconhighlightedCallback != null) {
                rcMap.rowIconhighlightedCallback(this_.lat_ + "," + this_.lon_, false, true);
            }
            rcMap.highlightMarker(this_.lat_+","+this_.lon_, false, true);
        });

        // Add the element to the "overlayImage" pane.
        var panes = this.getPanes();
        panes.overlayMouseTarget.appendChild(this.div_);
    };
</script>
<script nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
            
            RCMap.prototype.zoomOnSelectedLocation = true;
            

            RCMap.prototype.drawMap = function(){

                var mapStyles = this.mapStyles;
                var mapContainer = this.mapContainer;
                var mapIdleCallback = this.mapIdleCallback;
                var this_ = this;
                if(this_.drawOutsideLocations){
                    this_.outsideLocations.init();
                }


                var googleMap = new google.maps.Map(this.mapContainer.get(0), this.mapOptions);
                this.setMap(googleMap);

                if (this.drawPlaces) {
                    this.placesService = new google.maps.places.PlacesService(this.googleMap);
                }

                if(this.elementDataList.length == 0){
                    var geocoder = new google.maps.Geocoder();
                    var address=this.city+','+this.country;
                    geocoder.geocode( {'address' : address}, function(results, status) {
                        if (status == google.maps.GeocoderStatus.OK) {
                            googleMap.setCenter(results[0].geometry.location);
                            googleMap.fitBounds(results[0].geometry.bounds);
                        }
                    });
                }
                else{

                    
                    var elementDataList = this.elementDataList;
                    var selectedElement;
                    for (var i = 0; i < elementDataList.length; i++) {
                        var elementData = elementDataList[i];
                        if (elementData.selected) {
                            this.setSelectedElement(elementData);
                        } else if (!elementData.closed && elementData.groupedElements != null && elementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
                            for (var j = 0; j < elementData.groupedElements.length; j++) {
                                var subElement = elementData.groupedElements[j];
                                if (subElement.selected) {
                                    this.setSelectedElement(subElement);
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    

                    this.drawPricePinsOnMap();

                }

                if(this.zoomOnSelectedLocation){
                    var selectedPosition;
                    var elementDataList = rcMap.getElementDataList();
                    for (var i=0; i< elementDataList.length; i++) {
                        var elementData = elementDataList[i];
                        if (elementData.selected) {
                            selectedPosition = elementData.marker.getPosition();
                        }
                    }

                    googleMap.setCenter(selectedPosition);
                }
                else{
                    googleMap.fitBounds(this.bounds);
                }

                var zoomListener = google.maps.event.addListenerOnce(googleMap, 'bounds_changed', function(event) {
                    if(googleMap.getZoom() > 14){
                        googleMap.setZoom(14);
                    }
                    google.maps.event.removeListener(zoomListener);
                });

                var idleEventListener = google.maps.event.addListener(this.googleMap, 'idle', function(event) {

                    if(this_.drawOutsideLocations){
                        this_.outsideLocations.draw();
                    }

                    if(mapIdleCallback!=null){
                        mapIdleCallback();
                    }

                    if(this_.mapLoaded){
                        RCMap.track('userInteraction','idle');
                    }

                    if(!this_.mapLoaded){
                        this_.mapLoaded = true;
                    }

                });

                var zoomChangeEventListener = google.maps.event.addListener(this.googleMap, 'zoom_changed', function(event) {
                    if(this_.mapLoaded){
                        RCMap.track('userEvent','zoom_changed');
                    }
                });

                var centerChangeEventListener = google.maps.event.addListener(this.googleMap, 'center_changed', function(event) {
                    if(this_.mapLoaded){
                        RCMap.track('userEvent','center_changed');
                    }
                });

                var leftClickEventListener = google.maps.event.addListener(this.googleMap, 'click', function(event) {
                    if(this_.mapLoaded){
                        RCMap.track('userEvent','click');
                    }
                });

                var rightClickEventListener = google.maps.event.addListener(this.googleMap, 'rightclick', function(event) {
                    if(this_.mapLoaded){
                        RCMap.track('userEvent','rightclick');
                    }
                });

                if (rcMap.drawPlaces) {
                    var drawPOIListener = google.maps.event.addListenerOnce(this.googleMap, 'bounds_changed', function (event) {
                        this_.drawPOI();
                        google.maps.event.removeListener(drawPOIListener);

                    });
                }

                
                google.maps.event.addListener(googleMap, 'zoom_changed', function(event) {
                    if(rcMap.arePinsGrouped() && googleMap.getZoom() >= rcMap.getUngroupZoom()){
                        setGroupedPinVisibility(true);
                    } else if(!rcMap.arePinsGrouped() && googleMap.getZoom() < rcMap.getUngroupZoom()){
                        setGroupedPinVisibility(false);
                    }
                });
                

                this.originalBounds = this.bounds;

            }

            RCMap.prototype.resetMapPosition = function() {
                if(this.zoomOnSelectedLocation){
                    var selectedPosition;
                    var elementDataList = rcMap.getElementDataList();
                    for (var i=0; i< elementDataList.length; i++) {
                        var elementData = elementDataList[i];
                        if (elementData.selected) {
                            selectedPosition = elementData.marker.getPosition();
                        }
                    }

                    rcMap.googleMap.setCenter(selectedPosition);
                }
                else{
                    this.googleMap.fitBounds(this.originalBounds);
                }

                if(this.googleMap.getZoom() > 14){
                    this.googleMap.setZoom(14);
                }

                return false;
            }
        </script>

    rcMap.setPoiInfoWindowContentCallBack(poiInfoWindowContentCallBack);

                #map_location .pricePinLabel,.pricePinLabelActive{white-space: nowrap;}
            </style>
<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">


    
    RCMap.prototype.createPriceLabel = function(elementData, labelClass, pricePinZindex){
        if (!elementData.closed && !elementData.selected) {
            var labelText = "" + elementData.priceDifference;
        } else {
            var labelText = "" + elementData.fromPrice;
        }

        marker = new RCMap.MapLabel(elementData.lat, elementData.lon , labelText, labelClass, pricePinZindex, this.googleMap);

        return marker;
    }
    
    var pinLabelClassGrouped = "pricePinLabel aa-map__Pin_Grouped-Loc";
    var pinLabelClassActiveGrouped = "pricePinLabelActive aa-map__Pin_Grouped-Loc";

    function zoomToGroupedLocationLatLng(latLong) {
        var elementData = rcMap.getElementWithCoordinates(latLong, true);
        rcMap.googleMap.fitBounds(getGroupedElementBounds(elementData));
        var infoWindow = rcMap.infoWindow;
        if (infoWindow != null && typeof(infoWindow) != 'undefined' && rcMap.isInfoWindowOpen() && infoWindow.elementData!=null) {
            var latLongOld = infoWindow.elementData.lat+','+infoWindow.elementData.lon;
        }
        infoWindow.close();
        rcMap.rowIconhighlightedCallback(latLongOld, false, false);
        rcMap.highlightMarker(latLongOld, false, false);
    }

    function setGroupedPinVisibility(visible) {
        var elementDataList = rcMap.elementDataList;
        for (var i = 0; i < elementDataList.length; i++) {
            var elementData = elementDataList[i];
            if (!elementData.closed && elementData.groupedElements != null && elementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
                elementData.marker.setVisible(!visible);
                if (!visible ) {
                    elementData.marker.div_.className = 'pricePinLabel aa-map__Pin_Grouped-Loc';
                }
                var groupedElements = elementData.groupedElements;
                for (var j = 0; j < groupedElements.length; j++) {
                    if (!groupedElements[j].closed) {
                        groupedElements[j].marker.setVisible(visible);
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        rcMap.setPinsGrouped(!visible);
    }

    function getGroupedElementBounds(elementData) {
        var neLat = elementData.lat;
        var neLon = elementData.lon;
        var swLat = elementData.lat;
        var swLon = elementData.lon;

        if (elementData.groupedElements != null && elementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
            for (var i = 0; i < elementData.groupedElements.length; i++) {
                var subElement = elementData.groupedElements[i];
                if (subElement.lat > neLat) {
                    neLat = subElement.lat;
                } else if (subElement.lat < swLat) {
                    swLat = subElement.lat;
                }
                if (subElement.lon > neLon) {
                    neLon = subElement.lon;
                } else if (subElement.lon < swLon) {
                    swLon = subElement.lon;
                }
            }
        }

        var neLatLon = new google.maps.LatLng(neLat, neLon);
        var swLatLon = new google.maps.LatLng(swLat, swLon);

        return new google.maps.LatLngBounds(swLatLon, neLatLon);
    }

    RCMap.prototype.getUngroupZoom = function() {
        return this.ungroupZoom;
    }

    RCMap.prototype.setUngroupZoom = function(ungroupZoom) {
        this.ungroupZoom = ungroupZoom;
    }

    RCMap.prototype.arePinsGrouped = function() {
        return this.pinsGrouped;
    }

    RCMap.prototype.setPinsGrouped = function(pinsGrouped) {
        this.pinsGrouped = pinsGrouped;
    }

    RCMap.prototype.getSelectedElement = function() {
        return this.selectedElement;
    }

    RCMap.prototype.setSelectedElement = function(selectedElement) {
        this.selectedElement = selectedElement;
    }

    RCMap.prototype.openInfoWindowWithCoordinates = function(coordinates){
        var allElementData = this.elementDataList;
        var myElementData, subElementData;
        for (var i=0; i < allElementData.length; i++) {
            myElementData = allElementData[i];
            if (myElementData.groupedElements != null && myElementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
                for (var j = 0; j < myElementData.groupedElements.length; j++) {
                    subElementData = myElementData.groupedElements[j];
                    var elementDataLatLog = subElementData.lat + ',' + subElementData.lon;
                    if (elementDataLatLog == coordinates) {
                        this.openInfoWindow(subElementData);
                        break;
                    }
                }
            } else {
                var elementDataLatLog = myElementData.lat + ',' + myElementData.lon;
                if (elementDataLatLog == coordinates) {
                    this.openInfoWindow(myElementData);
                    break;
                }
            }
        }
    }

    RCMap.prototype.getElementWithCoordinates = function(coordinates, getParent){
        var allElementData = this.elementDataList;
        var myElementData;
        for (var i=0; i < allElementData.length; i++) {
            myElementData = allElementData[i];
            var elementDataLatLong = myElementData.lat+','+myElementData.lon;
            if(elementDataLatLong == coordinates && ((myElementData.parentCoords == null && myElementData.groupedElements == null) || (myElementData.groupedElements != null && (rcMap.arePinsGrouped() || getParent)))){
                
                    return myElementData;
                    
            }
            if (myElementData.groupedElements != null && myElementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
                var subElement;
                for (var j = 0; j < myElementData.groupedElements.length; j++) {
                    subElement = myElementData.groupedElements[j];
                    elementDataLatLong = subElement.lat+','+subElement.lon;
                    if(elementDataLatLong == coordinates){
                        return subElement;
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    RCMap.prototype.drawPricePinsOnMap = function(){
        var elementDataList = this.elementDataList;
        var pricePinZindex = elementDataList.length * 2;//space for grouped pins, first few indexes are reserved for POI and closed locations etc
        var googleMap = this.googleMap;
        var this_ = this;

        for(var i=0; i<elementDataList.length; i++){

            var elementData = elementDataList[i];

            var isAirport = elementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("airport") >= 0;
            var isTrainStation = elementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("train_station") >= 0;
            var pinIcon = '';
            var hoverPinIcon = '';

            if(elementData.closed && isAirport){
                pinIcon = this.closedAirportIcon;
            }
            else if (!elementData.closed && isAirport){
                pinIcon = this.pinAirportIcon;
                hoverPinIcon = this.pinAirportHoverIcon;
            }
            else if(elementData.closed && !isAirport){
                pinIcon = this.closedIcon;
            }
            else if(!elementData.closed && !isAirport){
                pinIcon = this.pinIcon;
                hoverPinIcon = this.pinHoverIcon;
            }

            var marker = this.createMarker(elementData, pinIcon, hoverPinIcon, pricePinZindex);
            pricePinZindex-- ;
            this.bounds.extend(marker.getPosition());

            if (elementData.groupedElements != null && elementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
                for (var j = 0; j < elementData.groupedElements.length; j++) {
                    var subElementData = elementData.groupedElements[j];

                    var isAirport = subElementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("airport") >= 0;
                    var isTrainStation = subElementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("train_station") >= 0;
                    var pinIcon = '';
                    var hoverPinIcon = '';

                    if (subElementData.closed && isAirport) {
                        pinIcon = this.closedAirportIcon;
                    }
                    else if (!subElementData.closed && isAirport) {
                        pinIcon = this.pinAirportIcon;
                        hoverPinIcon = this.pinAirportHoverIcon;
                    }
                    else if (subElementData.closed && !isAirport) {
                        pinIcon = this.closedIcon;
                    }
                    else if (!subElementData.closed && !isAirport) {
                        pinIcon = this.pinIcon;
                        hoverPinIcon = this.pinHoverIcon;
                    }

                    var marker = this.createMarker(subElementData, pinIcon, hoverPinIcon, pricePinZindex);
                    pricePinZindex--;
                    this.bounds.extend(marker.getPosition());
                }
            }

        }

        if(this.longLatPin!=null){
            var longLatPin = this.longLatPin;
            var marker = new RCMap.MapMarker(longLatPin.coordinates.lat, longLatPin.coordinates.lon, longLatPin.icon, longLatPin.name, 3, this_.googleMap, "mapMarkerLatLong");
            this_.bounds.extend(marker.getPosition());
        }
    }

    RCMap.prototype.createPriceLabel = function(elementData, labelClass, pricePinZindex){

        var labelText = "" + elementData.fromPrice;
        var isParent = false;
        var isChild = false;

        
        if (!elementData.closed && !elementData.selected) {
            labelText = elementData.priceDifference;
        }
        

        if (elementData.groupedElements != null && elementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
            labelText = "<span class='aa-map__Grouped-Loc-text'>"+labelText+"</span><span class='aa-map__Grouped-Loc-icon'></span>";
            labelClass = pinLabelClassGrouped;
            isParent = true;
        } else if (elementData.parentCoords != null) {
            isChild = true;
        }

        

        marker = new RCMap.MapLabel(elementData.lat, elementData.lon, labelText, labelClass, pricePinZindex, this.googleMap);
        marker.isParent = isParent;
        marker.isChild = isChild;
        

        return marker;
    }

    RCMap.prototype.createMarker = function(elementData, pinIcon, hoverPinIcon, pricePinZindex){
        var googleMap = this.googleMap;
        var this_ = this;
        var marker;

        var isTrainStation = elementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("train_station") >= 0;
        var isAirport = elementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("airport") >= 0;

        var activePinLabel;
        var pinLabel;
        
        if (elementData.groupedElements != null && elementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
            activePinLabel= pinLabelClassActiveGrouped;
            pinLabel = pinLabelClassGrouped;
        } else {
            activePinLabel = this.pinActiveLabelClass;
            pinLabel = this.pinLabelClass;
        }

        if(!this.drawPricePins){
            var zindex = 10;
            if (elementData.closed) {
                zindex = 2;
            }
            marker = new RCMap.MapMarker(elementData.lat, elementData.lon, pinIcon, elementData.name, zindex, googleMap);
            marker.hoverIcon = hoverPinIcon;
        }
        else if(elementData.selected && !elementData.closed){

            var labelClass = activePinLabel;
            var zIndex = google.maps.Marker.MAX_ZINDEX + 1;

            marker = this.createPriceLabel(elementData, labelClass, zIndex);
            marker.hoverIcon = hoverPinIcon;
        }
        else if(elementData.closed){
            marker = new RCMap.MapMarker(elementData.lat, elementData.lon, pinIcon, elementData.name, 2, googleMap);
            marker.hoverIcon = hoverPinIcon;
        }
        else{
            var labelClass = pinLabel;
            marker = this.createPriceLabel(elementData, labelClass, pricePinZindex);
            marker.hoverIcon = hoverPinIcon;
        }

        elementData.marker = marker;

        if( infoWindowContentCallBack && infoWindowContentCallBack!=null){
            google.maps.event.addListener(marker,"click",function(e) {
                if (e.target.className == 'aa-map__Grouped-Loc-icon') {
                    zoomToGroupedLocationLatLng(elementData.lat+","+elementData.lon);
                    RCMap.track('markerClick', 'mainMarker');
                } else {
                    var found = $('.stage .result').filter(function() {
                        return $(this).hasClass('active-location');
                    });
                    found.removeClass('active-location');
                    this_.openInfoWindow(elementData);
                    RCMap.track('markerClick', 'mainMarker');
                }
            });
        }

        if (elementData.selected) {
            
            elementData.marker.labelClass_ = activePinLabel + " selectedLocation";
            
        }

        return marker;

    };

    RCMap.prototype.highlightGroupedMarkers = function(latLong, highlight, checkInfoWindow) {
        var allElementData = this.elementDataList;
        for (var i=0; i < allElementData.length; i++) {
            var myElementData = allElementData[i];
            var elementDataLatLog = myElementData.lat+','+myElementData.lon;
            if(elementDataLatLog == latLong){
                if (myElementData.groupedElements != null && myElementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
                    for (var j = 0; j < myElementData.groupedElements.length; j++) {
                        rcMap.modifyMarker(myElementData.groupedElements[j], latLong, highlight, checkInfoWindow);
                    }
                }
                rcMap.modifyMarker(myElementData, latLong, highlight, checkInfoWindow);
            }
        }
    };

    RCMap.prototype.highlightMarker = function(latLong, highlight, checkInfoWindow){
        var elementData = this.getElementWithCoordinates(latLong);
        var infoWindow = this.infoWindow;
        var this_ = this;

        if (elementData != null && infoWindow != null) {
            var activePinLabel;
            var pinLabel;

            var myMarker = elementData.marker;
            var currentMarkerIcon = elementData.marker.div_.getElementsByTagName('img')[0];
            var isTrainStation = elementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("train_station") >= 0;
            var isAirport = elementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("airport") >= 0;

            if(highlight){ //highlighting
                if (!elementData.closed && this.drawPricePins) {
                    var labelClass = activePinLabel;
                    myMarker.setClass(labelClass);
                }
                if (myMarker.hoverIcon) {
                    currentMarkerIcon.src = myMarker.hoverIcon;
                }

                myMarker.setZIndex(google.maps.Marker.MAX_ZINDEX + 1);
            }
            else{ //back to normal again#
                if(elementData.closed && !this.drawPricePins){
                    myMarker.setZIndex(myMarker.getOriginalZIndex());
                }
                else{
                    if(checkInfoWindow && typeof(infoWindow) != 'undefined' && this_.isInfoWindowOpen() && infoWindow.elementData!=null ){//checkInfoWindow is used when you hover out of a location
                        var latLongInfoWindow = infoWindow.elementData.lat+','+infoWindow.elementData.lon;
                        if(latLong != latLongInfoWindow){//only unhighlight if infowindow not already open
                            var labelClass = pinLabel;

                            myMarker.setClass(labelClass);
                            myMarker.setZIndex(myMarker.getOriginalZIndex());

                            if (myMarker.hoverIcon) {
                                currentMarkerIcon.src = myMarker.icon_;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    else{
                        if(!elementData.selected){
                            var labelClass = pinLabel;
                            myMarker.setClass(labelClass);
                            myMarker.setZIndex(myMarker.getOriginalZIndex());
                        }

                        if (myMarker.hoverIcon) {
                            currentMarkerIcon.src = myMarker.icon_;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    RCMap.prototype.modifyMarker = function(myElementData, latLong, highlight, checkInfoWindow) {
        var infoWindow = this.infoWindow;
        var this_ = this;
        var myMarker = myElementData.marker;

        var activePinLabel;
        var pinLabel;
        
        if (myElementData.groupedElements != null && myElementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
            activePinLabel= pinLabelClassActiveGrouped;
            pinLabel = pinLabelClassGrouped;
        } else {
            activePinLabel = this.pinActiveLabelClass;
            pinLabel = this.pinLabelClass;
        }
        

        var currentMarkerIcon = myMarker.div_.getElementsByTagName('img')[0];
        if(highlight){//highlighting
            if(!myElementData.closed && this.drawPricePins){
                var labelClass = activePinLabel;
                myMarker.setClass(labelClass);
            }
            if (myMarker.hoverIcon) {
                currentMarkerIcon.src = myMarker.hoverIcon;
            }

            myMarker.setZIndex(google.maps.Marker.MAX_ZINDEX + 1);
        }
        else {
            if (myElementData.closed || !this.drawPricePins) {
                myMarker.setZIndex(myMarker.getOriginalZIndex());
            }
            else {

                if (checkInfoWindow && typeof(infoWindow) != 'undefined' && this_.isInfoWindowOpen() && infoWindow.elementData != null) {//checkInfoWindow is used when you hover out of a location
                    var latLongInfoWindow = infoWindow.elementData.lat + ',' + infoWindow.elementData.lon;
                    if (latLong != latLongInfoWindow) {//only unhighlight if infowindow not already open
                        var labelClass = pinLabel;

                        myMarker.setClass(labelClass);
                        myMarker.setZIndex(myMarker.getOriginalZIndex());
                    }
                }
                else {

                    if (!myElementData.selected) {
                        var labelClass = pinLabel;
                        myMarker.setClass(labelClass);
                        myMarker.setZIndex(myMarker.getOriginalZIndex());
                    }
                }
            }

            if (myMarker.hoverIcon) {
                currentMarkerIcon.src = myMarker.icon_;
            }
        }
    }

    var highlightRowIcon = function(latLong,highlight,checkInfoWindow) {
        var elementData = rcMap.getElementWithCoordinates(latLong);
        if (elementData != null && elementData.parentCoords != null) {
            latLong = elementData.parentCoords;
        }
        var found = $('.stage .result .address_container').filter(function() {
            var data = $("input:hidden[name='locationLatLong']", this);
            if (elementData != null && elementData.parentCoords != null) {
                latLong = elementData.parentCoords;
            }
            return data.length > 0 && latLong == data.val();
        });

        if (found.length == 0) {
            return undefined;
        }
        var resultBox_s = found.closest('.result');
        if(!$(resultBox_s).hasClass('closed')){
            if (highlight){
                resultBox_s.addClass('active-location');
            }
            else {
                var infoWindow = rcMap.infoWindow;
                if(checkInfoWindow && typeof(infoWindow) != 'undefined' && rcMap.isInfoWindowOpen() && infoWindow.elementData!=null ){//checkInfoWindow is used when you hover out of a location
                    var latLongInfoWindow = infoWindow.elementData.lat+','+infoWindow.elementData.lon;
                    if(latLong != latLongInfoWindow) {//only unhighlight if infowindow not already open
                        resultBox_s.removeClass('active-location');
                    }
                }
                else{
                    resultBox_s.removeClass('active-location');
                }
            }
        }

    }

    RCMap.prototype.rowIconhighlightedCallback = null;
    RCMap.prototype.setRowIconHighlightCallback = function(rowIconhighlightedCallback){
        this.rowIconhighlightedCallback = rowIconhighlightedCallback;
    }
    rcMap.setRowIconHighlightCallback(highlightRowIcon);

    var scrollListToView = function(latLong){
        
                var found = $('.stage .result').filter(function() {
                    var data = $('input:hidden[name=locationLatLong]', this);
                    if (rcMap.getElementWithCoordinates(latLong).parentCoords != null) {
                        latLong = rcMap.getElementWithCoordinates(latLong).parentCoords;
                    }
                    return data.length > 0 && latLong == data.val();
                });

                if (found.length == 0) {
                    return;
                }

                // Using position instead of offset() gets scroll position relative to parent
                var scrollTo = found.position().top;
            

        $('body,html').animate({scrollTop:scrollTo});
        var resultBox = found.closest('.result');
        $({alpha:0.80}).animate({alpha:0}, {
            duration: 2000,
            step: function(){
                resultBox.css('-webkit-box-shadow',' 0px 0px 10px 2px rgba(72,154,227,'+this.alpha+')');
                resultBox.css('-moz-box-shadow',' 0px 0px 10px 2px rgba(72,154,227,'+this.alpha+')');
                resultBox.css('box-shadow',' 0px 0px 10px 2px rgba(72,154,227,'+this.alpha+')');
            },
            complete: function(){
                resultBox.css('-webkit-box-shadow','');
                resultBox.css('-moz-box-shadow','');
                resultBox.css('box-shadow','');
            }
        });
    }

    RCMap.prototype.openInfoWindow = function(elementData){
        var content = this.infoWindowContentCallBack(elementData);
        var marker = elementData.marker;
        var this_ = this;
        var infoWindow = this.infoWindow;

        if(infoWindow.elementData!=null && typeof(infoWindow.elementData) !== 'undefined'){
            var latLongOld = infoWindow.elementData.lat+','+infoWindow.elementData.lon;
            var checkInfoWindow = false;
            this_.highlightMarker(latLongOld,false, checkInfoWindow);
        }
        infoWindow.elementData = elementData;
        infoWindow.setContent(content);
        infoWindow.open(this.googleMap,marker);

        var latLong = elementData.lat+','+elementData.lon;
        this.highlightMarker(latLong,true);

        google.maps.event.addListener(this.googleMap, "click", function(){
            infoWindow.close();
            var checkInfoWindow = false;
            this_.rowIconhighlightedCallback(latLong, false, false);
            this_.highlightMarker(latLong, false, checkInfoWindow);
        });

        google.maps.event.addListener(infoWindow, "closeclick", function(){
            var checkInfoWindow = false;
            this_.rowIconhighlightedCallback(latLong, false, false);
            this_.highlightMarker(latLong, false, checkInfoWindow);
        });

        google.maps.event.addListener(this.googleMap, 'zoom_changed', function(event) {
            if(elementData.parentCoords != null && rcMap.googleMap.getZoom() < rcMap.getUngroupZoom() ||
                elementData.groupedElements != null && rcMap.googleMap.getZoom() >= rcMap.getUngroupZoom()){
                infoWindow.close();
                var checkInfoWindow = false;
                this_.rowIconhighlightedCallback(latLong, false, false);
                this_.highlightMarker(latLong, false, checkInfoWindow);
            }
        });
    }

    var infoWindowContentCallBack = function(elementData){
        console.log('2');
        var isAirport = elementData.locType.toLowerCase().indexOf("airport") >= 0;

        if(elementData.closed){
            var content = $('#map_location > .info_gls_wrapper.closed-loc').clone();
            $('.name', content).html(elementData.name);
            $('#info_window_closing_time_monday', content).html(elementData.openingTimes.monday);
            $('#info_window_closing_time_tuesday', content).html(elementData.openingTimes.tuesday);
            $('#info_window_closing_time_wednesday', content).html(elementData.openingTimes.wednesday);
            $('#info_window_closing_time_thursday', content).html(elementData.openingTimes.thursday);
            $('#info_window_closing_time_friday', content).html(elementData.openingTimes.friday);
            $('#info_window_closing_time_saturday', content).html(elementData.openingTimes.saturday);
            $('#info_window_closing_time_sunday', content).html(elementData.openingTimes.sunday);
        }
        else if(zeroResults){
            var content = $('#map_location > .info_gls_wrapper.open-loc').clone();
            $('.name', content).html(elementData.name);
            $('.location-stats', content).hide();
            $('.address', content).html(elementData.address);
            $('.buttons a', content).attr('href',elementData.action);
            $('.buttons a', content).html(editableMessage.search);
            $('.buttons a', content)[0].setAttribute('onclick',"RCMap.trackTransition('searchFromPin','zero_results')");//cannot attach onclick using jquery so using pure js
        }
        else{
            var content = $('#map_location > .info_gls_wrapper.open-loc').clone();
            $('.name', content).html(elementData.name);
            $('.map-pin-popout-price strong', content).html(elementData.fromPrice);
            if(!isAirport){
                $('.address', content).html(elementData.address);
            }

            $('.buttons a', content).attr('href',elementData.action);
            $('.buttons a', content)[0].setAttribute('onclick',"RCMap.trackTransition('searchFromPin','closed_location')");//cannot attach onclick using jquery so using pure js

            

            if (elementData.groupedElements != null) {
                $('.header-location-count strong', content).html(elementData.groupedElements.length);
            } else {
                $('.header-location-count strong', content).html(1);
            }
            $('.header-companies-count strong', content).html(elementData.companies);
            $('.header-car-count strong', content).html(elementData.numCars);

            if (elementData.groupedElements != null && elementData.groupedElements.length > 1) {
                $('.header-location-count small', content).html(editableMessage.locations);
            } else {
                $('.header-location-count small', content).html(editableMessage.location);
            }

            if(elementData.companies == 1){
                var supplierText = editableMessage.supplier;
                $('.header-companies-count small', content).html(supplierText);
            }
            else{
                var supplierText = editableMessage.suppliers;
                $('.header-companies-count small', content).html(supplierText);
            }

            if(elementData.numCars == 1){
                var carsText = editableMessage.car;
                $('.header-car-count small', content).html(carsText);
            }
            else{
                var carsText = editableMessage.cars;
                $('.header-car-count small', content).html(carsText);
            }

            // include car count on button
            if (elementData.numCars > 1) {
                $('.buttons .singular-button-text', content).hide();
                $('.buttons .car-count', content).html(elementData.numCars);
            } else {
                $('.buttons .plural-button-text', content).hide();
            }
        }

        return content.html();
    }

    rcMap.setInfoWindowContentCallBack(infoWindowContentCallBack);

    var redrawLocationsAfterZoom = function(){

        var foundOpenLoc = false;
        var foundClosedLoc = false;
        var resultZero = true;
        var googleMap = rcMap.getMap();
        var allElementData = rcMap.getElementDataList();
        for (var i=0; i < allElementData.length; i++) {
            var myElementData = allElementData[i];
            var elementDataLatLog = myElementData.lat+','+myElementData.lon;
            var myMarker = allElementData[i].marker;
            var found = $('.stage .result').filter(function() {
                var data = $("input:hidden[name='locationLatLong']", this);
                return data.length > 0 && elementDataLatLog == data.val();
            });
            if (googleMap.getBounds().contains(myMarker.getPosition()) ){
                found.show();
                resultZero = false;
                if(zeroResults){
                    if(myElementData.closed){
                        foundClosedLoc = true;
                    }
                    else{
                        foundOpenLoc = true;
                    }
                }
            } else {
                found.hide();
            }

            if (!myElementData.closed && myElementData.groupedElements != null && myElementData.groupedElements.length > 1 && (!rcMap.arePinsGrouped())) {
                var foundOpenChild = false;

                for (var j=0; j < myElementData.groupedElements.length; j++) {
                    var subElement = myElementData.groupedElements[j];
                    var parentElementDataLatLog = myElementData.lat+','+myElementData.lon;
                    var myMarker = subElement.marker;
                    var found = $('.stage .result').filter(function() {
                        var data = $("input:hidden[name='locationLatLong']", this);
                        return data.length > 0 && parentElementDataLatLog == data.val();
                    });
                    if (googleMap.getBounds().contains(myMarker.getPosition()) ){
                        foundOpenChild = true;
                        resultZero = false;
                        if(zeroResults && !subElement.closed){
                            foundOpenLoc = true;
                        }
                    }
                }

                if (foundOpenChild) {
                    found.show();
                } else {
                    found.hide();
                }
            }
        }

        if(resultZero){
            $('.stage .result').show();
        }

        if(zeroResults){
            if(foundOpenLoc){
                $('.stage h2.sub-heading.open-loc').show();
            }
            else{
                $('.stage h2.sub-heading.open-loc').hide();
            }
            if(foundClosedLoc){
                $('.stage h2.sub-heading.closed-loc').show();
            }
            else{
                $('.stage h2.sub-heading.closed-loc').hide();
            }
        }

        var infoWindow = rcMap.getInfoWindow();
        if(rcMap.isInfoWindowOpen() && typeof(infoWindow.elementData) !== "undefined" && infoWindow.elementData != null){
            var latLog = infoWindow.elementData.lat+','+infoWindow.elementData.lon;
            scrollListToView(latLog);

        }
    }
    

    rcMap.drawMap();

    

    var documentReadyFunction = function(){

        $('.stage .result a.show_on_map').click(function() {
            var data = $(this).closest('.result').find("input:hidden[name='locationLatLong']");
            var latLong = data.val();
            rcMap.openInfoWindowWithCoordinates(latLong);
            
        });

        


        $('.search-filter-map a').click(function() {
            $('body,html').toggleClass('filter');
            $('body,html').animate({scrollTop:0});
            

            if ($('body').hasClass('filter')) {
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'MapAllAreas', 'Search&Filter', 'open' , 1, true);
            } else {
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'MapAllAreas', 'Search&Filter', 'close' , 1, true);
            }
        });
        $('.bui-search-toggle').click(function() {
            $('body,html').toggleClass('filter');
            $('body,html').animate({scrollTop:0});
            

            if ($('body').hasClass('filter')) {
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'MapAllAreas', 'Search&Filter', 'open' , 1, true);
            } else {
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'MapAllAreas', 'Search&Filter', 'close' , 1, true);
            }

            $('.bui-filter-closed').toggleClass('bui-hide');
            $('.bui-filter-closed').toggleClass('bui-show');
            $('.bui-filter-open').toggleClass('bui-show');
            $('.bui-filter-open').toggleClass('bui-hide');

        });

        $('.search-filter a').click(function() {
            
            $('body,html').toggleClass('filter');
            
        });

        

        $('.stage .car-result').each(function(){
            var coordinates = $(this).find('input:hidden[name=carCoordinates]');
            var latLong = coordinates.val();

            $(this).find('.result_pickup p').click(function(){
                rcMap.openInfoWindowWithCoordinates(latLong);

            });
        });
        $(".carResultRow_OfferInfo_SupplierLocation_PickUp a, .carResultRow_OfferInfo_SupplierLocation_DropOff a").dotdotdot({height:36});
    }

    $(document).ready(documentReadyFunction);

    </script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
    /* UtmzUtils */
    (function() {

        var utmzCookieValues = null;

        function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
            var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
            return val;
        }

        function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
            if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
                return utmzCookieValues;
            }
            else {
                var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
                if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
                    var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
                    var ga = {};
                    for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
                        var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
                        ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
                    }
                    utmzCookieValues = ga;
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
                else {
                    utmzCookieValues = {};
                    return utmzCookieValues;
                }
            }
        }

        function getValue(name) {
            var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
            return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
        }

        window.UtmzUtils = {
            getValue: getValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
            _getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
        };

    })();
</script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="qvadh4gc9mqunv15v3tpf9051o">
                function tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, substringTerms) {
                    var tagIncludesSubstring = false;
                    $.each(substringTerms, function(index, term) {
                        if (typeof tag.src != undefined && tag.src.indexOf(term) !== -1) {
                            tagIncludesSubstring = true;
                            return false; // breaks $.each loop
                        }
                    });

                    return tagIncludesSubstring;
                }

                function getGoogleMapCountFromTags(tags) {
                    var cnCountryOfResidence = false;
                    var googleMapUrls = cnCountryOfResidence ? ['maps.google.cn'] : ['maps.googleapis.com', 'maps.google.com'];

                    var googleMapCount = 0;
                    $.each(tags, function(index, tag) {
                        if (tagSrcIncludesPathSubstring(tag, googleMapUrls)) {
                            googleMapCount++;
                        }
                    });
                    return googleMapCount;
                }

                $(document).ready(function() {
                    var scriptTags = document.scripts;
                    var imgTags = document.images;

                    var googleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(scriptTags);
                    var staticGoogleMapCount = getGoogleMapCountFromTags(imgTags);

                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'GoogleMapScriptCount', 'PN:search-results:'+googleMapCount, 1, true);
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'ErrorDebugInfo', 'StaticGoogleMapImageCount', 'PN:search-results:'+staticGoogleMapCount, 1, true);
                });
			</script>
